leaders we might come away from a study of the Renaissance ready

00:17:15.500 --> 00:17:18.100
as all the great Renaissance figures would have wanted us to be

00:17:18.380 --> 00:17:20.400
to do the thing that really matters,

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:23.280
